**, and other tank-heavy compositions.\n- **Evelynn** counters: **Xayah and Vi**, skill shots from marksman and melee champions.\n- **Stress Test Composition** counters: **Axe and Blitzcrank** compositions that focus on heavy dueling and early pressure.\n\n## Conclusion\nWith a focused build and strategic placement, you can maximize the potential of your champions in a Challenger-rank match. Prioritize strong initial ranks and then focus on key items and composition adjustments to dominate mid and late games."}, "traceback": null, "children": [], "date_done": "2025-12-10T15:43:01.621007+00:00", "task_id": "dc7603f8-1423-495e-a50f-eefe5f3dd461"}